<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8" standalone="no"?><?Xpress productLine="ncc-clause" ?><clause id="_519803b3-ad51-489e-ba6f-34a37eb36d20" outputclass="ncc-clause" variation="NT"><sptc>13.4.6</sptc><title id="_1721ce0a-b8f8-4111-afb1-e126ffe1415c">Construction of ceilings, walls and floors</title><archive-num>New for 2022</archive-num><subclause id="_b3f07757-1d0f-4b6b-a689-109b22f441ce" outputclass="subclause"><title id="_e5ffc341-4e9d-4ec3-9344-a309336ea4da">SubClause</title><num>1</num><p>Ceilings, walls, floors and any opening such as a <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/1c3f2f74-4ee1-4cdd-b1b4-53c91069d002/1525_29.1.0.xml#_e797f2c4-257d-40ed-b823-43c65f2c0f2c" id="_6a57ed25-9dff-4102-b817-d2907afe88c7" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="glossterm">window</xref> frame, door frame, <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/1c3f2f74-4ee1-4cdd-b1b4-53c91069d002/1441_5.5.0.xml#_923cc200-bcae-4fb3-b11c-bf5caaab1c5f" id="_53221b7b-0ded-48ba-aab6-3d8af6ae93ae" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="glossterm">roof light</xref> frame or the like must be constructed to minimise air leakage in accordance with (2) when forming part of the external fabric a <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/1c3f2f74-4ee1-4cdd-b1b4-53c91069d002/1225_1.8.0.xml#_6f4c27ea-b6b3-468c-9ff4-72d533d9d0a2" id="_b050e331-d91d-4313-bc0c-474e223f11e2" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="glossterm">conditioned space</xref>.</p></subclause><subclause id="_d2f4eecc-2509-4f00-8a97-4c1cd3ce3e37" outputclass="subclause"><title id="_ae0d3a29-d2b7-4205-b5ce-5fa3a38de5ff">SubClause</title><num>2</num><p>Construction <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/1c3f2f74-4ee1-4cdd-b1b4-53c91069d002/1432_4.0.0.xml#_a5b45a91-1ac3-44a8-8644-acfc09c225a9" id="_9de7ada6-5fe2-4712-ac6e-dadc8d7d06cd" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="glossterm">required</xref> by (1) must be—</p><ol outputclass="alpha"><li id="_fc3b49a8-298a-4b99-89cd-2569877d22e9">enclosed by internal lining systems that are close fitting at ceiling, wall and floor junctions; or</li><li id="_a86eb057-103c-48ab-95d3-82bdc29cabbe">sealed at junctions and penetrations with—<ol><li id="_faed7bf4-4bf1-4bcb-a731-95babd852164">by close-fitting skirting, architraves, cornices; or</li><li>expanding foam, rubber compressive strip, or caulking, or the like.</li></ol></li></ol></subclause></clause>